6	Order Status	Intent = order_status	Ask for order number + flag for human follow-up	{"type": "intent", "intent": "order_status"}	{"type": "ask_order_number", "flag_human": true}	t	6	2026-05-25 10:52:27.486227	2026-06-12 13:46:55.022699
